Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.modeldata

Record Class GamePhaseData

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
it.polimi.ingsw.client.modeldata.GamePhaseData
Record Components:
gameState - state of the game
turnState - state of the turn
currPlayerNickname - nickname of the current player
lastRound - flag that says if it is the last round or not
activatedCharacter - active character card
activatedCharacterPunctualEffectApplied - flag that says if the effect of the active character card has been applied or not
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public record GamePhaseData(GameState gameState, TurnState turnState, String currPlayerNickname, boolean lastRound, CharacterID activatedCharacter, boolean activatedCharacterPunctualEffectApplied) extends Record implements Serializable
contains the information about the phase of the game
